dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_Parcels_2016.gdb. Additional features included in this geodatabase are 'FARMLAND' and 'GENERAL' zoning information, and the table 'TX00MC_2015'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data for this county, please visit: https://gis-scccdd.opendata.arcgis.com/
